    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>quick</strong> <strong>dry brined chicken</strong>, skin-side down and cook for 10 min or until the skin has browned and crisped</p>",
