    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced cucumber</strong> to a small bowl with<strong> </strong>your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, mix everything together and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
