      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>Texas-style toast</strong> into triangles and slice the <strong>Texas-style dalmatian chicken </strong>into halves</p><p>Serve the <strong>Texas-style toast</strong> <strong>slices </strong>with the <strong>Texas-style dalmatian chicken</strong>, <strong>slaw</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong> to the side</p><p>Add the <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> to a little pot for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
